description._content: Description: Kartaldagh Forest. Aleppo pine self-sown seedlings, under mature trees; Kartaldagh Forest Northern Range; Before removal of old trees. Location: Kartaldagh, Cyprus Date: 1920-1930 Description: Kartaldagh Forest. View of Yaila, natural regeneration in foreground. Location: Kartaldagh, Cyprus Date: 1920-1930 Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/697 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives.
